    "description": "Tuck into the ultimate Christmas sarnie. Load your toasted baguette with turkey, crispy bacon, stuffing and cranberry mayo, then top with crispy onions and serve with thin and crispy salt and vinegar spuds. Festive, fancy and downright delicious.",
